# 🎓 College AI Agent

## 📌 Project Description
This project is an AI-powered assistant designed for a college website. It handles queries related to admissions, courses, fees, scholarships, and policies using structured and unstructured data sources.

---

## 🧠 Architecture Overview

The system follows a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) approach:

User → NLP → Intent Classification → Routing → Retrieval → Validation → Response

